<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc6e1005-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s1b"><num value="1b">§ 1b.</num><heading> Countersignature of certificate of election</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The certificate mentioned in <ref href="/us/usc/t2/s1a">section 1a of this title</ref> shall be countersigned by the secretary of state of the State.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc6e1006-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(R.S. § 19.)</sourceCredit>
